            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/01/new-study-shows-59-of-tuna-sold-in-the-u-s-isnt-tuna/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on New Study Shows 59% of &#8220;Tuna&#8221; Sold in the U.S. Isn&#8217;t Tuna"><span>5</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/escolar/" rel="tag">Escolar</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/food-fraud/" rel="tag">Food Fraud</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/kimberly-warner/" rel="tag">Kimberly Warner</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/oceana/" rel="tag">Oceana</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/stealth-inflation/" rel="tag">Stealth Inflation</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/the-atlantic/" rel="tag">The Atlantic</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/white-tuna/" rel="tag">White Tuna</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/01/new-study-shows-59-of-tuna-sold-in-the-u-s-isnt-tuna/#comments">20</a> 
